data.description: Potentially assumable loan at 5.25%! You won't be disappointed in this beautiful home. Located on a corner lot in a lovely newer neighborhood in Veneta, this home with 4 true bedrooms and a main level den that could be a 5th bedroom has room for everyone. This home has been meticulously maintained, and has original upgrades including quartz countertops, and tile flooring.  The main floor is an open and spacious great room, with a large living room, dining area, and kitchen with cherry cabinets and big pantry.  Through the slider in the dining area you'll find a covered patio, landscaped yard complete with raised gardens.  Upstairs the utility area is convenient to the 4 bedrooms which includes a luxurious primary suite with soaking tub, step in shower, and huge walk in closet.  Lots to love in this home and neighborhood! All inspections have been done and all of the recommended repairs are complete making for a smooth transaction!
